      "featuredOnHome": true,
      "fullDescription": "Project Edtech is an innovative initiative designed to transform STEM education through technology-driven solutions. We are building a comprehensive platform that leverages AI, data analytics, and interactive tools to create personalized learning experiences for students worldwide. Our mission is to democratize access to high-quality STEM education and empower educators with the tools they need to inspire the next generation of innovators.\n\nWe are actively hiring talented individuals across multiple disciplines—including software engineers, product managers, curriculum designers, educators, data scientists, and more. Whether you're a developer passionate about edtech, an educator with innovative ideas, or a strategist who wants to scale educational impact globally, we want to hear from you!\n\nJoin us in reshaping how students learn STEM.",
      "shortDescription": "Project Edtech is transforming STEM education through technology-driven solutions. We're hiring across multiple roles—engineers, educators, designers, and strategists. Help us democratize access to quality STEM learning worldwide."
    }
